Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.board.placeables

Class Placeable

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.board.placeables.Placeable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Block, Dome, Worker
public abstract class Placeable
extends java.lang.Object
This class is the superclass of Block, Dome, Worker. Informally: They are the only "things" that can be put on the Cells of the Board.
Author:
Giorgio Corbetta
